snippet.textDisplay: Can someone with insider knowledge explain to me, why it had to be Idina for Elsas Singing? I know this is subjective and I am not saying this to offend, but I really could have thought of so many better singers than her for elsa. She is much too "masculine", her voice doesn't have that subtleness, curiousity, that icey feeling. She could sing a barmaid in Beauty and the beast tbh. And her high tones are often more or less screamed/ yelled.
